LUS instead of IPLUS when args are integers, and it does the "right" thing when they are notWorkaround: Test Case: Edit-By: le.pasaEdit-Date: 16-Aug-84 13':52':23Attn: Kaplan, MasinterAssigned To: In/By: Disposition: System: Programming EnvironmentSubsystem: DWIMMachine: Disk: Microcode Version: Memory Size: File Server: Server Software Version: Difficulty: ModerateFrequency: EverytimeImpact: ModeratePriority: PerhapsStatus: OpenProblem Type: BugSource Files: 